    excerptEn: `The natural translucency of certain stones allows designers to create stunning backlit installations impossible to achieve with any other material. Slab stone backlighting has become enormously popular in modern interiors, used in walls, kitchen countertops, bathrooms, and narrow corridors. This article covers the four critical factors you must consider for successful slab stone lighting.`,
