    excerptEn: `Azna stone is one of the world's most well-known and widely used crystal stones, bearing a very close visual resemblance to marble. Its brilliant transparency and exceptional light-reflectivity make it a popular and affordable alternative to marble in smaller projects. This article explores the characteristics, applications, advantages, disadvantages, and pricing of Azna crystal stone.`,
