    excerptEn: `Granite slab stone has been making its way into luxury homes and commercial facilities for centuries, used in every corner of the home from kitchen countertops to flooring and wall cladding. Granite slabs are available in a wide range of designs and colors at affordable prices. This guide covers everything you need to know about granite slab stone.`,
